--- a/HANDOFF.md
+++ b/HANDOFF.md
@@ -41,6 +41,69 @@ were confirmed already deployed and the first admin already bootstrapped.
 
 ---
 
+## Batch 2 (same June 18 session — second round of fixes)
+
+1. **Feedback: all fields mandatory; date auto-applied.** Every rating (1–5),
+   both text fields and the name are required to submit; the manual date input
+   was removed and the date is stamped automatically at submission. Student
+   name is locked to their session. (`pals_forms_portal.html`)
+2. **Certificate hidden from students.** Removed the Certificate tab from the
+   student forms-portal view and the cert quick-card from the student hub —
+   instructors issue certificates. (`pals_forms_portal.html`, `hub_student.html`)
+3. **More 3/4 ↔ 9 dedup.** Module 4's IO slide (duplicated Module 9's IO
+   landmark image + text) is now a shock-context IV-vs-IO decision slide that
+   defers landmark/technique to Module 9; Module 3's BVM card now points to
+   Module 9 for OPA/C-E technique. (`slides/pals_module_04_shock…`, `…module_03…`)
+4. **Cohort isolation ("can't be mixed") — UI + rules ("Both").**
+   - Hub roster: a cohort selector scopes roster, stats and CSV export to one
+     cohort at a time (persisted); roster merge now carries real student fields
+     (exam-unlock, feedback, scores). (`hub_instructor.html`)
+   - `firestore.rules`: admins & lead instructors see all cohorts; a plain
+     `instructor` can only read/write users + students in their **own** cohort
+     (student cohort resolved from the user profile — no duplication). Plain-
+     instructor roster load was adapted to cohort-scoped queries so it stays
+     rules-compatible. **Deploy needed:** `firebase deploy --only firestore:rules`.
+   - Note: the instructor *dashboard* still does unconstrained collection reads —
+     fine for admin/lead (Nitai); a plain instructor would see it empty and
+     should use the hub roster instead.
+
+---
+
+## Batch 3 (bug-fix round)
+
+1. **Pre-test now hidden (not just locked)** until all 9 modules are complete —
+   student tabs are fully dynamic; the Pre-Test tab and hub card only appear
+   once modules are done. (`pals_forms_portal.html`, `hub_student.html`)
+2. **Admin "Reset Progress" actually clears** now — was `setDoc({progress:{}},
+   {merge:true})`, which deep-merges maps and left the old keys (student still
+   read as complete). Switched to `updateDoc` (overwrites the field).
+   (`hub_instructor.html`)
+3. **Every submitted form embeds the current date, non-editable** — pre-test,
+   attendance, BLS, megacode, final-exam and certificate date fields are
+   auto-set to today, `readOnly`, `min=max=today`. (`pals_forms_portal.html`;
+   feedback was already auto.)
+4. **Dashboard roster edit fixed** — a stray quote in the edit button's
+   `onclick` (`…')'"`) broke every edit; removed. (`pals_instructor_dashboard.html`)
+5. **Instructors now appear in the roster** — dashboard no longer filters the
+   roster to students-only (enrolled stat + cohort progress still count
+   students only). Plus: creating an account now refreshes the hub roster
+   immediately, and the success panel has an **✉ Email login details** button
+   (mailto with the sign-in link + credentials pre-filled — true server-side
+   email needs a backend, which this static site doesn't have).
+   (`pals_instructor_dashboard.html`, `hub_instructor.html`)
+6. **Removed non-essential bits** — "Export JSON" (forms pre-reg + dashboard
+   "Export All Forms"), and the QR-share buttons.
+7. **QR audit** — removed the forms-portal QR buttons (they encoded the
+   auth-gated portal URL, i.e. instructor-only). The course-planner QR points
+   to the public, un-gated planner page, so it was left as-is.
+
+**Still open from the handoff list (NOT done — need source material / large
+content effort):** audit modules 01–02 & 04–08, per-slide quizzes for all
+decks, full cross-module see-also pass, AHA 2025 errata (needs the reference
+PDFs Nitai holds locally). Cross-module pointers were added for M3/M4 ↔ M9.
+
+---
+
 ## Repo state
 
 **Repo:** `mavreg7/PALS_course` · `main` auto-deploys to Vercel on push.
